{
  "stem": "10588.12",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And I believe that this influenced me so that till this day, when I-- I would never go gamble in a casino.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "I don't want to leave my life in the hands of chance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I want to be in control of my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "Because 19-- from September 1, 1939, when the Germans, Germany invaded Poland, till I was liberated during Passover, April 26, 1945, by the Swedish Red Cross, I have seen all those values that my family taught me.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I remembered one thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I don't want to leave to chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because regardless of what I do or who told me what to, the consequences are mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I cannot afford to lose two things-- my life, my self-respect, my dignity, and my freedom.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On those things, I do not take a chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that story is always connected, and with clothes, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- Returning to your Jewish school, do you remember the teachers?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was a naughty girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when they spoke in Yiddish and tell stories about Jewish history and everything, I was interested.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I had to make prayers, and I didn't understand yet what they meant, I never wanted to say something unless I understood it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I felt a little re-- reluctant to do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And but nevertheless, I've learned how to write Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Till this day, I know how to write Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And looking back, my family and my religion had the greatest impact on me, really.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because-- and the reason why it is, because I grew up in a home where there were diet-- the kosher dietary laws.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then there was a restriction, as you all know-- the ones who know about Jewish laws-- that after meat, you have to wait six hours til you can eat dairy, after dairy, a half an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So even if I wanted to do it, I couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I learned to say no to myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, it influenced me because whenever there was a holiday, my-- I saw the rituals. and being born during Passover, heard the many stories.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every year I heard the prayers-- next year in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I did not-- it never entered my mind that I will be one who will live to see after two thousand year, you know, to see the rebirth of our-- of Israel, you know, in 1948.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just-- it grieves me that my family did not survive to see this year and so many others.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it is because what they were not privileged to do that I came here for those who-- well, not privileged.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the Israelites were in, in, in Egypt, by Pharaoh, and when they were li-- when they were liberated, with-- prayed-- before they were liberated, prayed, my people go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now we pray, let my people know what's happened to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can tell you this, that the anti-Jewish laws during Pharaoh pale in comparisons with the law that's happened during Hitler.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because Pharaoh just singled out Jewish male children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Hitler singled out all Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And not only did he single them out for dead and they legalized murder, that to, to murder-- to murder, mass murder of the Jews was legal.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But for a Jew to survive, even a child, was illegal and punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was still not the worst.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The worst was that they tried to dehumanize us and destroy our image of ourself and of God by telling us that we are subhuman, that we are vermin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we came to the concentration camps, and for those who were fortunate enough to be taken into the camp, they put on tattoos, like this here.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from then on, the did-- they always called [NON-ENGLISH], which means prisoner, 25673.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was my number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And whenever they did that, I said always under my breath, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Itka-- ?] because that's what my family called me-- I said, I am not a numbers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Numbers cannot feel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They cannot think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They cannot act.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He saved so many Jewish people because he cared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the other hand, the Nazi doctor, Josef Mengele, is responsible for the death of over 400,000 people, including thousands of people from the ghetto [INAUDIBLE] where I was before I came to Auschwitz-Birkenau and my entire family.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I have seen that men can be creators and destroyers of life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have the potential for both.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the difference is how much do we care.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Understand?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here was a Jewish bakery.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the name of the bake-- the man who had the bakery was [?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
